# LIKEPASS Project Rules

- TypeScript strict mode; avoid `any`
- Validate inputs with Zod
- Authorization on server, not UI only
- Ranking logic in pure functions under `src/server/services/ranking/`
- External services via adapter interfaces (`src/lib/ai/`, `src/lib/r2/`)
- Do not leak locked ranking image URLs or content IDs to unauthenticated/unvoted clients
- Never commit secrets
